WEBVTT

00:02:31.763 --> 00:02:32.906
With high-speed cameras,

00:02:32.930 --> 00:02:34.961
we can do the opposite of time lapse.

00:02:34.985 --> 00:02:36.306
We can shoot images

00:02:36.330 --> 00:02:38.779
that are thousands of times
faster than our vision.

00:02:41.001 --> 00:02:44.961
And we can see how nature's
ingenious devices work,

00:02:44.985 --> 00:02:47.143
and perhaps we can even imitate them.

00:02:50.648 --> 00:02:52.641
When a dragonfly flutters by,

00:02:52.665 --> 00:02:54.700
you may not realize,

00:02:54.724 --> 00:02:56.923
but it's the greatest flier in nature.

00:02:56.947 --> 00:02:59.439
It can hover, fly backwards,